stalled and authenticated\\nE2E_AGENT=claude-code go test -tags=e2e ./cmd/entire/cli/e2e_test/...\\n\\n# Run a specific test\\nE2E_AGENT=claude-code go test -tags=e2e -run TestE2E_BasicWorkflow ./cmd/entire/cli/e2e_test/...\\n```\\n\\nE2E tests:\\n\\n- Use the `//go:build e2e` build tag\\n- Located in `cmd/entire/cli/e2e_test/`\\n- Test real agent interactions (Claude Code, Gemini CLI, or OpenCode creating files, committing, etc.)\\n- Validate checkpoint scenarios documented in `docs/architecture/checkpoint-scenarios.md`\\n- Support multiple agents via `E2E_AGENT` env var (`claude-code`, `gemini`, `opencode`)\\n\",\"numLines\":70,\"startLine\":1,\"totalLines\":619}},\"sourceToolAssistantUUID\":\"8d5b4018-89c3-4718-b3f9-b22e433f1692\"}\n{\"parentUuid\":\"894cf1b9-7d3c-46bb-9025-705e29927ac3\",\"isSidechain\":false,\"userType\":\"external\",\"cwd\":\"/Users/robin/Developer/cli\",\"sessionId\":\"0a6fa8ce-14c1-4d76-b8cd-3e2d721777e9\",\"version\":\"2.1.49\",\"gitBranch\":\"rwr/cursor-docs\",\"slug\":\"serialized-growing-starfish\",\"message\":{\"model\":\"claude-opus-4-6\",\"id\":\"msg_01Q96uxj2baDBgAZFaU7uEra\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"id\":\"toolu_012gyc59HHcUKu5Gw44fXirY\",\"name\":\"Edit\",\"input\":{\"replace_all\":false,\"file_path\":\"/Users/robin/Developer/cli/CLAUDE.md\",\"old_string\":\"- `entire/cli/agent`: agent implementations (Claude Code, Gemini CLI) - see [Agent Integration Checklist](docs/architecture/agent-integration-checklist.md) and [Agent Implementation Guide](docs/architecture/agent-guide.md)\",\"new_string\":\"- `entire/cli/agent`: agent implementations (Claude Code, Gemini CLI, OpenCode, Cursor) - see [Agent Integration Checklist](docs/architecture/agent-integration-checklist.md) and [Agent Implementation Guide](docs/architecture/agent-guide.md)\"},\"caller\":{\"type\":\"direct\"}}],\"stop_reason\":null,\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":1,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":11